or bypath that check, knowing &#39;sudocommand=sudo -i&#39;.
I have two instances of SE, the one that works is
[root@srm1 ~]# rpm -qf /etc/bestman2/conf/bestman2.rc
bestman2-client-2.3.0-16.osg.el5
bestman2-server-2.3.0-16.osg.el5
